      "docs": "Top-level trait implementation record (ADR 2026-05-20-0048 D1/D2). action: ItemAction declares the TDDD operation for this impl entry (Add/Modify/Reference/Delete); serde default is Add so the field may be omitted in JSON when Add is intended. trait_ref (TypeRef, full path with generics) and for_type (TypeRef, implementing type) replace old trait_name/origin_crate/generic_args/for_ fields. impl_generics and impl_where_predicates carry impl-block-level type parameters and constraints (IN-06). Instances live top-level on CatalogueDocument.trait_impls (D1), not per-TypeEntry. action field and DTO TraitImplDto.action implemented at f048be4 (T013/T014/T015 done). Real inherent new() method declared per IN-18 for symmetric comparison (IN-17).",
